{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-a-graphic-using-css","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"applied-visual-design","demoType":null,"title":"Napravite grafiku koristeci CSS","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Menjanjem razlicitih selektora i svojstava mozete napraviti zanimljive oblike. Jedan od najjednostavnijih za probu je oblik polumeseca. U ovom izazovu koristite <code>box-shadow</code> svojstvo koje dodaje senku elementu, kao i <code>border-radius</code> svojstvo koje kontrolise zaobljenje uglova elementa.</p>\n<p>Napravicete kruzni element, providan, sa ostrijom senkom blago pomerenom u stranu, a ta senka ce zapravo formirati oblik polumeseca.</p>\n<p>Da biste napravili kruzni element, <code>border-radius</code> treba postaviti na vrednost 50%.</p>\n<p>Možda se sećate iz prethodnog izazova da <code>box-shadow</code> prima vrednosti <code>offset-x</code>, <code>offset-y</code>, <code>blur-radius</code>, <code>spread-radius</code> i <code>color</code> tim redosledom. Vrednosti <code>blur-radius</code> i <code>spread-radius</code> su opcione.</p>\n</section>","id":"587d78a6367417b2b2512add","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Izmenite kvadratni element u editoru kako biste napravili oblik meseca. Prvo promenite <code>background-color</code> u <code>transparent</code>, zatim postavite <code>border-radius</code> na 50% da biste dobili kružni oblik. Na kraju promenite <code>box-shadow</code> tako da <code>offset-x</code> bude 25px, <code>offset-y</code> 10px, <code>blur-radius</code> 0, <code>spread-radius</code> 0 i <code>color</code> bude <code>blue</code>.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":"https://scrimba.com/c/cEDWPs6","superBlock":"responsive-web-design","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301048,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-a-graphic-using-css"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<style>\n  .center {\n    position: absolute;\n    margin: auto;\n    top: 0;\n    right: 0;\n    bottom: 0;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100px;\n    height: 100px;\n    background-color: blue;\n    border-radius: 0px;\n    box-shadow: 25px 10px 10px 10px green;\n  }\n\n</style>\n<div class=\"center\"></div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Vrednost <code>background-color</code> svojstva treba da bude <code>transparent</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/background-color:\\s*?transparent;/gi);"},{"text":"<p>Vrednost <code>border-radius</code> svojstva treba da bude <code>50%</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/border-radius:\\s*?50%;/gi);"},{"text":"<p>Vrednost <code>box-shadow</code> svojstva treba da bude 25px za <code>offset-x</code>, 10px za <code>offset-y</code>, 0 za <code>blur-radius</code>, 0 za <code>spread-radius</code> i na kraju <code>blue</code> za <code>color</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.match(code,/box-shadow:\\s*?25px\\s+?10px\\s+?0(px)?\\s+?0(px)?\\s+?blue\\s*?;/gi);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/responsive-web-design/#applied-visual-design","dashedName":"create-a-graphic-using-css","certification":"responsive-web-design","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"applied-visual-design","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-a-more-complex-shape-using-css-and-html","prevChallengePath":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/use-the-css-transform-property-skewy-to-skew-an-element-along-the-y-axis","id":"587d78a6367417b2b2512add","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":0,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<style>\n  .balls {\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    position: fixed;\n    width: 50px;\n    height: 50px;\n    top: 60%;\n    animation-name: jump;\n    animation-duration: 2s;\n    animation-iteration-count: infinite;\n  }\n  #red {\n    background: red;\n    left: 25%;\n    animation-timing-function: linear;\n  }\n  #blue {\n    background: blue;\n    left: 50%;\n    animation-timing-function: ease-out;\n  }\n  #green {\n    background: green;\n    left: 75%;\n    animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(0.311, 0.441, 0.444, 1.649);\n  }\n\n  @keyframes jump {\n    50% {\n      top: 10%;\n    }\n  }\n</style>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"red\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"blue\"></div>\n<div class=\"balls\" id=\"green\"></div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/responsive-web-design/applied-visual-design/create-a-graphic-using-css"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}